This paper deals with the problem of dynamic routing in a communication network, which involves optimizing the choice of coding schemes based on various parameters. This problem is closely related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI), as well as control and optimization (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.MA), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
